description:
 summary: Build event management system for virtual speed dating and community events
 details: |
  Implement events platform:
  - Event creation and management (admin)
  - Event types: Speed Dating, Workshop, Community Chat
  - Capacity limits and registration
  - Event pricing (free for some, paid for premium)
  - Calendar view of upcoming events
  - Zoom/Jitsi integration for video events
  - Automated reminders before events
  - Post-event follow-ups
  - Event analytics and attendance tracking
  - Community building features

acceptance_criteria[10]:
 POST /api/events creates new event (admin)
 GET /api/events lists upcoming events
 POST /api/events/{id}/register registers user
 Registration respects capacity limits
 Paid events require valid subscription or payment
 Email reminders sent 24h and 1h before event
 Zoom link generated for virtual events
 Attendance tracked when users join
 Post-event survey sent to attendees
 Analytics show registration and attendance rates

